title: compilation error
body_html:
hello, I install the latest anaconda and follow the guide of code compilation steps showing on the github page, but frequently get the same error /libTH.so.1: undefined symbol: convolve_5x5_sse.
then I checkout the previous branch, named as origin/autograd_debug, this time the compilation is successful, I install it, but the code test is still frustrating, the libTH.so.1 still has the same error.

import torch
Traceback (most recent call last):
File "", line 1, in
File "/home/j/anaconda2/lib/python2.7/site-packages/torch/init.py", line 53, in
from torch._C import *
ImportError: /home/j/anaconda2/lib/python2.7/site-packages/torch/lib/libTH.so.1: undefined symbol: convolve_5x5_sse

call for help!

body:
hello, I install the latest anaconda and follow the guide of code compilation steps showing on the github page, but frequently get the same error /libTH.so.1: undefined symbol: convolve_5x5_sse. 
then I checkout the previous branch, named as origin/autograd_debug, this time the compilation is successful, I install it, but the code test is still frustrating, the libTH.so.1 still has the same error.
>>> import torch
Traceback (most recent call last):
  File "<stdin>", line 1, in <module>
  File "/home/j/anaconda2/lib/python2.7/site-packages/torch/__init__.py", line 53, in <module>
    from torch._C import *
ImportError: /home/j/anaconda2/lib/python2.7/site-packages/torch/lib/libTH.so.1: undefined symbol: convolve_5x5_sse
>>> 
call for help!
